{"tid":716862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墨西哥大選前再有鎮長候選人遇刺　全鎮27名警員及部長涉案就逮","createTime":"2018-06-25T15:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T01:05:29.000Z","uid":53379,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"17a5247461634cc013536888d28916ab1c34b0c9","tid":716862,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T15:29:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">墨西哥大選前再有鎮長候選人遇刺　全鎮27名警員及部長涉案就逮</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180625/s00005/220f867ed3a0d94a4b10aeb9c0a83f68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180625%2Fs00005%2F220f867ed3a0d94a4b10aeb9c0a83f68.jpg&h=0fe85986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - 市內警局全體27名警員和公共安全部長涉案被捕。（Twitter圖片/明報製）<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥米卻肯州奧坎波（Ocampo）一名鎮長候選人上周遭槍殺，是一星期內州內第三名政客遇刺。當局調查發現，鎮上警局全體27名警員和公共安全部長涉案，周日（24日）拘捕他們。<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥7月1日舉行大選，選出總統、參議員及地方首長等。選前全國已有逾百名政客及候選人被殺，堪稱墨西哥現代史上最血腥一屆大選。64歲奧坎波鎮長候選人華雷斯（Fernando &Aacute;ngeles Ju&aacute;rez），上周四（21日）準備出席競選活動前，在酒店外中槍死亡。<br />\n<br />\n華雷斯是一名成功商人，可是從政經驗少，本想以獨立候選人身分參選，最後決定加入墨西哥主要政黨、中間偏左的民主革命黨。他好友說，華雷斯參選是因看見當地極為貧窮、社會不平等及貪污。<br />\n<br />\n華雷斯死後，檢控當局調查後認為，奧坎波公共安全部長加西亞（Oscar Gonz&aacute;lez  Garc&iacute;a）涉案，指控他勾結州內黑幫。墨西哥聯邦人員上周六（23日）到奧坎波拘捕加西亞時，受當地警員阻撓。翌日早上，聯邦人員增援再回來，拘捕全鎮27名警員及他們的上司，綁上索帶帶走問話。<br />\n<br />\n（英國廣播公司/路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180625/s00005/1529921051308\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180625%2Fs00005%2F1529921051308&d=6u3WKRALOrPV2yHo7GhbizA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=95e1d49a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180625%2Fs00005%2F1529921051308&h=f01db338\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180625/s00005/1529921051308</a>"},{"pid":"04e450b928e858b4c829e5addd3591bef679617b","tid":716862,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/715606/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/715606/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b82accf72ee7d77d39803c7eee1b6b711d0e5f","tid":716862,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6039855462427c4864545c031356862489f8e8","tid":716862,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"墨西哥好波<br />\nwe love mexico<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d84bf6206febed7064eb19b82711f3b8179a3fe","tid":716862,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T17:32:55.000Z","msg":"衰過支那"},{"pid":"15d2ed68a294c96158b69c8a01b31e5afcfd49d1","tid":716862,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T17:39:28.000Z","msg":"未選都死左過百人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d233f88a87a1ac0416fc6a2a6a76a7a96438f120","tid":716862,"uid":34852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"墨西哥從政=自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df4cfc024fb0185b5be6aee25c9424113d9e7cc","tid":716862,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:14:58.000Z","msg":"墨西哥真係要核平"},{"pid":"81df2cc5276c15f32a704442644911fba7977d78","ti